" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安裝 WINDOWS 7時, 裝到第2步 &quot;正在展開windows檔案&quot; 然後出現下列錯誤訊息<br />\n<br />\n&quot;windows無法安裝所需檔案，檔案已損毀或遺失，請確定安裝所需的檔案均可使用， 錯誤碼︰ 0x80070017&quot;<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n經過反覆測試發現, 主要是讀不到安裝所需的檔案,可以依序用下列方法解決:<br />\n<br />\n1.光碟片不良: 重燒寫一次或換其它光碟片. 重燒時要注意, 如果燒出來的光碟片安裝一樣錯誤時, 則使用不同的倍數或不同台光碟機去重燒寫.<br />\n<br />\n2.光碟機不良: 換台光碟機試試,最好用燒光碟片的那台. 我自己遇到的就是光碟機讀取不良會挑片造成.<br />\n<br />\n3.記憶體不良: 可以用記憶體測試軟體, 一支一支測試記憶體, 如果沒有測試軟體, 那就輪流拔插記憶體再安裝WIN7測試了."},{"pid":"c87064225830e705890423ecc1c06cc2bbd70e21","tid":333842,"uid":130278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:23:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去到呢個位卡住點算？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/24/160541_12c5950ce5c332b708760da8300b3663.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F160541_12c5950ce5c332b708760da8300b3663.jpg&h=126a13b2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n新底版同win7唔兼容<br />\nps. 尻估<br />\n<br />\n我之前試過一樣情況，搞撚左成日，download個win8即刻裝到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41be6438dd764f45c9676c7a218226c795c3af8f","tid":333842,"uid":42229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去到呢個位卡住點算？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/24/160541_12c5950ce5c332b708760da8300b3663.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F24%2F160541_12c5950ce5c332b708760da8300b3663.jpg&h=126a13b2&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n新底版同win7唔兼容<br />\nps. 尻估<br />\n<br />\n我之前試過一樣情況，搞撚左成日，download個win8即刻裝到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係 轉裝win10就搞掂"},{"pid":"974ab2000f84aa6a2a657330bd41810ee401b88d","tid":333842,"uid":130278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB